    SFMT32 (SIMD-oriented Fast Mersenne Twister 32bit version) The original program, SFMT, is provided under 3-clause BSD license. The copyright holders of the original SFMT programs are Matsuo Saito, Makoto Matsumoto, Hiroshima University and The University of Tokyo. See Lisence.txt of SFMT programs. http://www.math.sci.hiroshima-u.ac.jp/~m-mat/MT/SFMT/
